WWW::Dropload version 0.1
=========================

DESCRIPTION

This module provides a perl API for uploading files to dropload.com.

DOCUMENTATION

The documentation is in Dropload.pm in the form of POD format
perldocs. Please look there for an idea of what this module is 
capable of.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Carp
WWW::Mechanize

